    "Cine A F\u0103cut Propuneri Concrete Pentru A Se Ajunge la Un Acord PITTSBURGH Pa De partamentul de Justi\u0163ie a fcerut permisie de la tribunalul fede ral din Pennsylvania de apus ca s\u0103\u015fi retrag\u0103 cazul instituit \u00eempotriva lui Steve Nelson \u015fi contra celorlal\u0163i 5 conduc\u0103tori comuni\u015fti condamna\u0163i sub le gea anticonstitu\u0163ional\u0103 Smith Dl Malcolm Anderson rep rezent\u00eend Departamentul de Justi\u0163ie al \u0163\u0103rii \u00een acest district a luat ac\u0163iunea aceasta pe baza deciziei Cur\u0163ii Supreme din vara trecut\u0103 \u015fi pe faptul c\u0103 tribunalul federal a fost ordo nat s\u0103 revizuie cazul Tribunalul federal a acordat permisiunea Departamentului de Justi\u0163ie ca s\u0103 nu mai aduc\u0103 cazul din nou spre judecat\u0103 Pe baza eviden\u0163ei in posesia American Historian Reveals The Real Truth About Hungary By CYNTHIA MANN The peaceloving people of this country who suffered an intense emotional shock from last years events in Hungary would do well td read Herbert Apthekers recent book The Truth About Hungary Dr Apthekers treatment of the subject is thorough and his sources and references com pletely documented He delves into history and traces events in their chronological order The Sources While the spokesmen of those who would place all blame and onus on the government of Hungary"
